    <item>
      <title>德国联邦金融监管局表示，欧洲需要更简单而不是更宽松的金融规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/europe-needs-simpler-not-laxer-financial-rules-bafin-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高金融监管机构表示，欧盟需要不太复杂的监管来帮助银行和投资者为其经济改革提供资金，同时反对软化资本标准的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/europe-needs-simpler-not-laxer-financial-rules-bafin-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团退出钻石和铂金业务以抵御必和必拓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/anglo-to-exit-diamonds-and-platinum-in-bid-to-fend-off-bhp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团将退出钻石、铂金和煤炭开采业，进行大规模重组，旨在抵御竞争对手必和必拓集团 340 亿英镑（合 430 亿美元）的收购，并将该矿商转变为铜业巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/anglo-to-exit-diamonds-and-platinum-in-bid-to-fend-off-bhp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blackstone 将从德国 PBB 购买 9 亿欧元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/deutsche-pfandbriefbank-to-sell-900-million-in-us-uk-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blackstone Inc. 正在与 Deutsche Pfandbriefbank AG 洽谈购买 9 亿欧元（合 9.71 亿美元）的美国和英国贷款，这家德国房地产银行正努力应对房地产市场恶化的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/deutsche-pfandbriefbank-to-sell-900-million-in-us-uk-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 05:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
